Hi! I am a fourth-year student majoring in Statistics and Data Science as well as Global Studies at UCLA. After my graduation in June 2024, I will pursue a master degree in Data Science. At the same time, I am open to intern and full-time job opportunities. I am especially interested in roles like data analyst and data scientist. I believe my knowledge in machine learning, predictive analysis, data mining, sentiment analysis, alongside my skill sets in R, SQL, and Python, would make me a competitive candidate for these positions. Feel free to contact me!



University of California, Los Angeles - Los Angeles, CA
B.S. in Statistics and Data Science, B.A. in Global Studies Expected Jun 2024
Honor: Dean’s List for 5 quarters
GPA : 3.78/4.0



You can find the link to my project paper for data mining’s application in alcoholic status prediction.
